The paper presents a new model-based reinforcement learning algorithm for efficient learning in multi-agent Markov decision processes. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA), Robotics (cs.RO), and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
